name: Too Old to Die Young
overview: Detective Martin Jones, who leads a double life as a killer for hire in Los Angeles' deadly underground, suffers an existential crisis which leads him deeper into a blood splattered world of violence.

episodes.overview: A Los Angeles Sheriff's Deputy is slowly dragged into a dark underworld following a tragic shooting.

episodes.name: Volume 3: The Hermit
episodes.overview: Now a detective, Martin investigates a murder suspect who is not what he appears to be.

episodes.name: Volume 4: The Tower
episodes.overview: Viggo brings Martin under his wing, giving him a chance to prove himself.

episodes.name: Volume 5: The Fool
episodes.overview: Martin goes down a dark road while hunting two brothers in New Mexico.

episodes.name: Volume 8: The Hanged Man
